description:
The Free Planets Alliance battleship Gora-Daileng was flagship of the Free Planets Alliance 8th Fleet under the command of Vice Admiral Fang Tchewling. Pennant number 0801.
In the myths of the Caroline Islands, Gora-Daileng was the god of the nether world who punishes the sinners by pushing them in to his river which carried them down into a cave from whence they never returned.
Gineipedia
name: Gora-Daileng
